Mother;;2009;;R;;Crime,Drama,Mystery;;7.8;;Bong Joon Ho;;Hye-ja Kim,Won Bin,Jin Goo,Je-mun Yun,Mi-seon Jeon,Sae-byeok Song,Yeong-seok Lee,Hee-ra Mun,Woo-hee Chun,Byoung-Soon Kim,Moo-yeong Yeo,Yeong-gi Jeong,Go Gyu-pil,Mi-do Lee,Jin-gu Kim,Hong-jib Kim,Kyung Jin Min,Kyeong-sook Jo;;A mother lives quietly with her twenty-eight-year-old son, Do-joon, providing herbs and acupuncture to neighbors. One day, a girl is brutally murdered, and Do-joon is charged with the killing. Now, it's his mother's call whether to prove him innocent or to leave him imprisoned.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1216496/